definition:
Someone descended from Shimron who was a man of the tribe of Issachar living at the time of Egypt and Wilderness, first mentioned at Gen.46.13; 
 son of: Issachar (H3485); 
 brother of: Tola (H8439), Puah (H6312) and Jashub (H3437H)
Group of shim.ron (שִׁמְרוֹן "Shimron" H8110B) 
 § Shimronites, of Shimron "guardian"
 descendants of Shimron
